              span.thin-hero
                | coup
            h1.lead.center A simpler, more direct approach to connecting the biggest brands with the best content 
              | creators. Sign up now. 
          div.col-sm-2
        div.row.landing-body 
          div.col-lg-3
          div.col-lg-6
            <!-- Begin LaunchRock Widget -->
            div(id="lr-widget" rel="CE49GBNX")
